Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.53,0:00:23.77,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你个深井冰 是你挑事的 就是你\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}You crazy twat! You're taking the piss, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.77,0:00:27.25,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你个大蠢货 你现在把我们全拉下水了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}You stupid prick, you've dropped us all in the shit now,
