Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.13,0:00:45.63,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他只是去刺伤了一个人\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}He's only gone and stabbed someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.63,0:00:47.17,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是吧 愚蠢的疯子 给我闭嘴\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}hasn't he? Crazy twat. Just shut it.
