Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.53,0:00:52.29,正片中文,,0,0,0,,小心我下一秒就会刺你\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I'll stab you in a minute, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.37,0:00:56.81,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-科林 别说了 好么 -你要刺我\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Colin, just leave it out, yeah? You'll stab me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.81,0:00:58.73,正片中文,,0,0,0,,嘿 嘿 别打了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Hey! Hey, get off him!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.73,0:01:01.13,正片中文,,0,0,0,,开到路边 快开到路边\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Pull over! Pull over now!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.05,0:01:06.45,正片中文,,0,0,0,,滚 立马从车上下来 你待在车上\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Get out! Get out the car now! You stay there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.45,0:01:07.89,正片中文,,0,0,0,,冲着我来呗\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Come on then!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.89,0:01:09.25,正片中文,,0,0,0,,干嘛 你要干嘛\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.25,0:01:10.89,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他就是看我不顺眼 对么\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}He was looking at me, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.89,0:01:13.17,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-觉得我就像一坨屎 -那个在哪儿 -什么\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Looking at me like I'm shit! Where is it? What?!
