Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.29,0:01:35.85,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他杀了他了么\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Did he kill him?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.01,0:01:40.01,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-他杀死他了么 -我不知道\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Did you kill him?! I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.33,0:01:42.37,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-喂 -我是托尼\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}'Yeah?' It's Tony.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.37,0:01:43.81,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你个混蛋\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.81,0:01:46.77,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你让我给你收拾烂摊子 你个混蛋 麦凯布也是\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}You got off and left me to it, you prick. McCabe as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.77,0:01:49.53,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-他怎么样 -我不知道 我都不知道我干了什么\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}'How is he?' I don't know. I don't know what I'm doing, do I?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.53,0:01:52.65,正片中文,,0,0,0,,据我所知他会失血身亡的 你个混蛋\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}He could be bleeding to death for all I know, you prick.
