Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.60,0:02:46.06,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.73,0:02:54.29,正片中文,,0,0,0,,沃德太太么 是的\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Mrs Ward? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.29,0:02:56.05,正片中文,,0,0,0,,托马斯 沃德的母亲\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Mother of Thomas Ward?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.05,0:02:57.13,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.13,0:02:59.73,正片中文,,0,0,0,,沃德太太 我们受指令带你去皇家医院\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}We've been told to bring you down to the Royal, Mrs Ward.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.73,0:03:01.45,正片中文,,0,0,0,,托马斯出了一些小意外\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Thomas has had a bit of an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.45,0:03:03.01,正片中文,,0,0,0,,什么意外\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}What sort of accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.01,0:03:05.61,正片中文,,0,0,0,,亲爱的 我不知道 我们只是受命过来接你\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I don't know, love. We've just been told to come and get you.
