Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.89,0:03:09.05,正片中文,,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.77,0:03:13.53,正片中文,,0,0,0,,给我一分钟\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Just a sec.
