Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.21,0:03:45.37,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你还见他么\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Do you still see him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.37,0:03:46.73,正片中文,,0,0,0,,只在必要的情况下\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Only when I have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.77,0:04:11.01,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你好 我是玛格丽特 沃德\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Hello. I'm Margaret Ward.
