Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.29,0:04:21.33,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你等一下 我打个电话\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}If you just hang on, I'll make a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.01,0:04:25.53,正片中文,,0,0,0,,詹尼弗 嗨 这里是前台\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Jennifer? Hi, it's reception.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.53,0:04:27.01,正片中文,,0,0,0,,沃德太太到了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Mrs Ward is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.13,0:04:33.13,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-请问 发生了什么 -沃德太太\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}What is it, please? Mrs Ward?
