Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.61,0:04:37.08,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-沃德太太 -我是詹尼弗 菲尔丁\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I'm Jennifer Fielding, Mrs Ward.
