Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.73,0:04:42.25,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这儿过去有一间房间\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}There's a room just through here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.53,0:04:47.01,正片中文,,0,0,0,,请进来 沃德太太\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Come in, please, Mrs Ward.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.45,0:04:49.69,正片中文,,0,0,0,,请\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.65,0:05:05.61,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉 托马斯没有熬过去\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Thomas didn't make it, I'm afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.77,0:05:07.69,正片中文,,0,0,0,,熬过什么\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Make what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.97,0:05:11.73,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他今晚早些时候被刺伤了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}He was stabbed earlier this evening
