Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.05,0:05:15.29,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我非常抱歉\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.89,0:05:18.73,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我想你可能找错人了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I think you've got the wrong boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.77,0:05:21.25,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我是托马斯 沃德的妈妈\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I'm Thomas Ward's mother,
