Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.29,0:06:16.81,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你去哪儿了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Where you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.81,0:06:18.49,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-出去玩 -哪儿\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Out. Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.49,0:06:19.49,正片中文,,0,0,0,,只是出去玩了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Just out.
